---
title: Maple-Glazed Duck with Butternut Squash Wild Rice Pilaf
description: Rich, savoury duck and sweet, earthy maple syrup come together in this hearty and flavour-packed dinner. Butternut squash wild rice pilaf and crisp green beans round out a rustic, decadent experience you are sure to remember.

